  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You ward a creature within range against death. Make a DC 15 Spell Check.</p><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The next time the target takes damage that would reduce it to 0 HP, it gains 3 Temp HP before taking the damage and the Spell ends.</p><p><strong>Success:</strong> The target gains 4 Temp HP instead.</p><p><strong>Success (Each 5):</strong> +1 Temp HP.</p><p>If a creature is already on 0 HP or lower when this Spell is cast on it, the Spell activates when it next take damage instead.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Duration: (1 MP, Repeatable, Sustained)</strong> The duration is increased by 1 step (10 min → 1 hour → 8 hours → Long Rest).</p><p><strong>Additional Temp HP: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The target gains an additional 3 Temp HP.</p><p><strong>Doomed Protection: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Up to 2 stacks of Doomed ends on the creature.</p>",
